    public abstract class ReadOrWriteStage
extends TargetFullFeatureStage
    This is an abstract superclass for stages that handle PDUs with command descriptor blocks of the ReadOrWriteCdb class.
    Author:
    Andreas Ergenzinger

    • Method Detail

      • checkOverAndUnderflow

        protected void checkOverAndUnderflow(ReadOrWriteCdb cdb)
        Checks if the LOGICAL BLOCK ADDRESS and TRANSFER LENGTH fields in the passed ReadOrWriteCdb are acceptable. If illegal values are detected, an instance of FieldPointerSenseKeySpecificData describing the problem will be added to the ReadOrWriteCdb's queue-
        Parameters:
        cdb - a read or write command descriptor block to check
        See Also:
        CommandDescriptorBlock.getIllegalFieldPointers()
